SELECT t1.indistinct_id, MIN(f0_), GROUP_CONCAT_UNQUOTED(f1_, ","), GROUP_CONCAT_UNQUOTED(f2_, ",")

(SELECT t1.indistinct_id, MIN(t2.some_field), SUBSTR(GROUP_CONCAT(UNIQUE(t5.id)),0,1000)

  SELECT LOWER(LTRIM(RTRIM(indistinct_id))) as indistinct_id

) t1
JOIN (
  SELECT LOWER(LTRIM(RTRIM(id_map.indistinct_id))) as indistinct_id, MIN(redacted_ev.created) as some_field

    SELECT distinct_id, created

    WHERE created >= "2021-05-20 00:00:00"
  ) redacted_ev
  JOIN [redacted_project.redacted_dataset.identifier_mapping] AS id_map
    ON id_map.distinct_id = redacted_ev.distinct_id
  GROUP BY indistinct_id
) t2
ON t2.indistinct_id = t1.indistinct_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
  SELECT LOWER(LTRIM(RTRIM(indistinct_id))) as indistinct_id
  FROM [redacted_project.redacted_dataset.redacted_d_202111]
  WHERE created >= "2021-11-14 00:00:00" AND (subaction IN ("subaction_4750441586130944","subaction_4649308759687168","subaction_5303271417741312","subaction_6132349894033408"))
